NATIVE-DETAILS - Retrieve

Retrieve operation of resource: native-details

instance-name: string
in path

ID of instance-name

flex-alg: string
in path

ID of flex-alg

200 OK
native-details_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

PATHS - Retrieve

Retrieve operation of resource: paths

instance-name: string
in path

ID of instance-name

flex-alg: string
in path

200 OK
paths_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

in path

in path

200 OK

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json
Response Example (200 OK) 
{

"outgoing-label": "integer", SR-MPLS label

    
"backup-repair-list-size": "integer", Backup Repair List Size

"is-lc-disjoint": "boolean", Is the backup path line card disjoint with\nprimary?

    
"backup-repair": [No description

      {
        
"repair-s-rv6-end-func": "string", Repair SRv6 End Function

        
"repair-element-type": "integer", Repair Element Type

        
"repair-s-rv6sid": "string", Repair SRv6 SID

        
"repair-strict-spf-label": "integer", Repair Strict SPF Label

      }
    ],

TOPOLOGY-LEVEL - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-clns-isis-oper:isis/instances/instance/{instance-name}/topologies/topology/topology-levels/topology-level/{level}/

Retrieve operation of resource: topology-level

instance-name: string
in path

ID of instance-name

level: string
in path

ID of level

200 OK
topology-level_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error
